<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَفِي أَرْبَعِينَ:</span> مُسِنَّةٌ لَهَا سَنَتَانِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَفِي سِتِّينَ:</span> تَبِيعَانِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> ثُمَّ فِي كُلِّ ثَلَاثِينَ:</span> تَبِيعٌ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَفِي كُلِّ أَرْبَعِينَ:</span> مُسِنَّةٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَأَقَلُّ نِصَابِ الغَنَمِ:</span> أَرْبَعُونَ،<span style="color:#006d98"> وَفِيهَا:</span> شَاةٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span style="color:#006d98">مِنَ المَعْزِ:</span> لَهَا سَنَةٌ وَاحِدَةٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span style="color:#006d98">أَوْ جَذَعَةٌ مِنَ الضَّأْنِ:</span> لَهَا سِتَّةُ أَشْهُرٍ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَفِي مَائَةٍ وَإِحْدَى وَعِشْرِينَ:</span> شَاتَانِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَفِي مَائَتَيْنِ وَوَاحِدَةٍ:</span> ثَلَاثُ شِيَاهٍ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> وَفِي أَرْبَعِمائَةٍ:</span> أَرْبَعُ شِيَاهٍ.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> ثُمَّ فِي كُلِّ مَائَةِ شَاةٍ:</span> شَاةٌ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَالخِلْطَةُ <span style="color:#008000">(١)</span> - بِشَرْطِهَا - تُصَيِّرُ المَالَيْنِ كَالمَالِ الوَاحِدِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span style="color:#006d98"> تَجِبُ الزَّكَاةُ فِي كُلِّ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span style="color:#707070">[١]</span> مَكِيلٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) الخُلْطَةِ: بضم الخاء: الشركة. ينظر: المطلع ص ١٦١.</p> </div>